  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Heat the infused oil in the Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and garlic and saute until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the smoked salmon and shrimp and cook until the shrimp are pink.",
    "Add the white wine and chicken broth and bring to a boil.",
    "Add the toasted fregola and stir to combine.",
    "Transfer the Dutch oven to the preheated oven and bake for 20 minutes.",
    "Remove the Dutch oven from the oven and stir in the heavy cream and parmesan cheese.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste."
